===Proper noun===
'''Commonwealth of Independent States'''

#Successor to the [[Soviet Union]], this is a confederation of eleven former [[Soviet]] republics: [[Armenia]], [[Azerbaijan]], [[Belarus]], [[Georgia]], [[Kazakhstan]], [[Kyrgyzstan]], [[Moldova]], [[Russia]], [[Tajikistan]], [[Ukraine]], and [[Uzbekistan]].

